<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <%- include('includes/head') %>
    <title>Choose your country</title>
  </head>
  <body>
      <%- include('includes/menu-v2') %>
  <div class="text-center mb-4">
    <h1 class="h3 text-charcoal font-weight-light my-3 mx-4">
      From which country does your digital identity come ?
    </h1>
  </div>
  <div class="container-flags">
    <div class="d-flex flex-row justify-content-between flex-wrap">

    <% for(let i = 0; i < locals.countryList.length; i++) {%>
      <div class="country">
        <form
          action="https://eidas-bridge.docker.dev-franceconnect.fr/<%= locals.uid %>/login"
          method="POST"
        >
          <button
            id="country-<%= countryList[i].iso %>"
            type="submit"
            class="country-btn d-flex align-items-center"
            name="country"
            value= <%= countryList[i].iso %>
          >
          <img src="<%= countryList[i].icon %>"/>
          <span class="m-0 d-block text-charcoal h6 font-weight-bold"><%= countryList[i].name %></span>
             
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>

    <%}%>
    </div>
    </div>
        <div class="ibid-container py-4 mt-5 mx-4">
          <p class="text-charcoal h6 font-weight-light">
            If your country is not on this list then the cross-border authentication option might not be available yet. If this is the case, then plus use
            <a class="text-charcoal" href="/">these other options</a>
            to access the servce. Your country will become available in the future? 
            <br/>
            <br/>
            <a class="text-charcoal" href="/">Learn more about the eIDAS regulation</a>
          </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
